    <item>
      <title>ACEA 表示，复活节提前导致 3 月份欧盟新车销量下降 5.2%</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/early-easter-causes-eu-new-car-sales-drop-52-march-says-acea-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲汽车行业机构周四表示，受复活节假期提前和市场影响，欧盟3月份新车销量同比下降5.2%，这是今年首次下降，也是2022年7月以来的最大降幅。经济低迷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/early-easter-causes-eu-new-car-sales-drop-52-march-says-acea-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 06:09:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
